br />\n1985年北京大學物理系本科畢業，1992年獲得美國愛荷華州立大學博士學位，曾任美國橡樹嶺國家實驗室傑出科學家，美國橡樹嶺國家實驗室中子散射科學部粉末衍射組負責人，美國田納西大學兼職教教授，承擔了美國國家科學基金會重大基金、美國能源部基礎研究基金、加拿大國家創新基金等重大課題（總經費2千餘萬美元）。<br />\n主要從事先進材料的力學性能、相變及磁學性能等領域的研究。在相關領域做出了傑出貢獻。曾經在《Science》、《Nature Materials》、《Advanced Materials》和《Physical Review Letters》等學術期刊上發表學術論文150餘篇，撰寫英文專著2部，並多次在國際會議上作特邀報告。獲TAPPI及ISCPPI最佳論文獎、工程材料研究重大事件獎、焊接學會的A.F. Davis銀獎等多項獎勵。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93a2638b272a41830124ed1e1af989b6be982c8","tid":163640,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:40:02.000Z","msg":"我屌撚晒你地老母呀 <br />\n你地班廢柴現實我一拳一件<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d56ff1e5bd4692cfa6e3ee917c15f2d2a95476","tid":163640,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:46:41.000Z","msg":"咁個迷團究竟係咩？？"},{"pid":"43b9c9a8c785f584cf5554c69f37207c9b6dbf39","tid":163640,"uid":18021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:56:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我屌撚晒你地老母呀 <br />\n你地班廢柴現實我一拳一件<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打算啦 <br />\n柒左就番去潛水啦<br />\nBtw買番本中文閱讀理解上堂睇下啦<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">柒頭</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaafa11fecc55acb5163f8b9252872368872ea20","tid":163640,"uid":5313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:20:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>比著hku 4年搞掂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nChing你中文拎幾多，人地話破解左科學界40年既謎團，唔係研究左40年喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" cla